OL,3,CMan 'chases car with hedge trimmer' at
OL,4,Cpetrol station
OL,6,FAn arrest has been made after footage
OL,7,Fappears to show a man chasing a car
OL,8,Fwith a hedge trimmer at a petrol
OL,9,Fstation.
OL,11,FThe incident, at the Shell garage on
OL,12,FRegent Road in Salford, happened on
OL,13,FMonday 5 August, Greater Manchester
OL,14,FPolice said.
OL,16,FThe video appears to shows a male in
OL,17,Fblack clothing running out of the
OL,18,Fpetrol station to fetch a hedge
OL,19,Ftrimmer from a white van before
OL,20,Fcharging towards another vehicle
OL,21,Fbrandishing the garden tool.
