OL,6,FThe driver of the other vehicle then
OL,7,Fspeeds out of the forecourt away from
OL,8,Fthe man.
OL,10,FA man in his 30s has been arrested on
OL,11,Fsuspicion of affray and remains in
OL,12,Fpolice custody, a spokesperson for the
OL,13,Fforce said on Wednesday.
OL,15,FThe social media footage, which was
OL,16,Foriginally shared on Instagram, was
OL,17,Fviewed 1.5 million times within a
OL,18,Fnumber of hours.
