OL,3,CMan 'chases car with hedge trimmer' at
OL,4,Cpetrol station
OL,6,FIn a statement, a Greater Manchester
OL,7,FPolice spokesperson said: "We were
OL,8,Fmade aware of a video circulating on
OL,9,Fsocial media which showed a man
OL,10,Fapproaching a vehicle in possession of
OL,11,Fa hedge trimmer on Monday evening (5
OL,12,FAugust 2024).
OL,14,F"Our officers acted swiftly and last
OL,15,Fnight (Tuesday 6 August 2024),
OL,16,Farrested a man in his 30s on suspicion
OL,17,Fof affray.
OL,19,F"He remains in police custody for
OL,20,Fquestioning and enquiries are ongoing."
